-- Bank of Canada Buys C$450 Million of Securities for One Day
-- B y   G r e g   Q u i n n
-- 2012-06-15T16:11:12Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-15/bank-of-canada-buys-c-450-million-of-securities-for-one-day.html
The Bank of  Canada  bought C$450
million ($439 million) of securities for one day.  The central bank announced the purchase, aimed to keep
overnight lending rates close to its current target of 1
percent, on its website today from Ottawa.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Greg Quinn in Ottawa at 
 gquinn1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Chris Wellisz at 
 cwellisz@bloomberg.net  